item.title: 【Requests】[REQ AUD] - No Rap Version of Keri Hilson's "Knock You Down"
item.description:
Hello everyone,

Does anyone have a No Rap Version of Keri Hilson's 2009 song "Knock You Down"? A few years ago, I heard a no rap version on the radio on New York's 95.5 WPLJ (now defunct). The version featured an instrumental intro instead of Kanye's intro and Kanye's rap verse was cut. The song was an edited version of the album version with Keri Hilson's bridge "So you gotta take the good with the bad..." coming after the second chorus.

I've been searching for this or a similar version for a while.
